        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow an increase in the limitation on the charitable contribution tax deduction for cash contributions made after August 23, 2019, and before January 1, 2020, for relief efforts related to Hurricane Dorian. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
